            "content": "\\[\n= \\frac {1}{2} \\int \\csc^ {3} x \\mathrm {d} x - \\frac {1}{2} \\int \\frac {\\mathrm {d} (\\sin x)}{\\sin^ {3} x} = \\frac {1}{2} \\int \\csc^ {3} x \\mathrm {d} x + \\frac {1}{4 \\sin^ {2} x},\n\\]"
