            "content": "由 \\([xy(x + y) - f(x)y]\\mathrm{d}x + [f'(x) + x^2 y]\\mathrm{d}y = 0\\) 为全微分方程得 \\(\\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = \\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial y}\\)"
