            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nf (x) = f (0) + f ^ {\\prime} (0) x + \\frac {f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (0)}{2 !} x ^ {2} + o \\left(x ^ {2}\\right) = \\frac {f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (0)}{2 !} x ^ {2} + o \\left(x ^ {2}\\right),\n\\]"
