            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.735,
                0.663,
                0.783
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(P\\{Z = 1\\} = 1 - P\\{Z = 0\\} = \\frac{3}{4}\\) 则 \\(Z\\) 的分布律为 \\(Z\\sim \\left( \\begin{array}{cc}0 & 1\\\\ \\frac{1}{4} & \\frac{3}{4} \\end{array} \\right).\\)"
